abstract: Stock market stabilizes due to rebound in health care sector, but overall gains are small.
lead_paragraph: Stocks made strong gains after an index of consumer confidence rose, but a rally at midday gave way to losses and trading was up and down after that.

headline.main: Market Steadies Itself, but Growth Jitters Return
headline.print_headline: Shares Take a Breather in Cautious Trading
